data.description: Start packing and come home to 2008 Whippoorwill Ave! This home has it all and you will be sure to fall in love with it! Located in Lakewood estates, walk through the front door to the living area with stone fireplace and built in bookcase! You wont run out of cabinet space in this kitchen...it features beautiful wood cabinets and granite counter tops, gas stove, breakfast bar and stone accents! Large second living room/game room or even additional bedroom. Current owners use it as a movie theater room and all theater equipment will stay with the property including sound equipment and the comfy chairs! Go out back to the back patio with wood accent ceiling and lots of space to entertain, barbeques and family gatherings. There is a small shop with electric that could be used for a man cave, she shed or personal storage! Owners suite is spacious with owners bath that includes whirlpool tub, open shower, dual vanity and two closets. 2 additional bedrooms with beautiful accent walls, main bath, laundry room with ample storage and a half bath for guests! The 2 car garage has an above ground safe room. Have you started packing yet? This home is perfect and well taken care of, you don't want to miss an opportunity to move to Lakewood Estates!
